E:  Ad=8a(I) Atr=02(Bulk) MxPS=  64 Ivl=0ms
E:  Ad=07(O) Atr=02(Bulk) MxPS=  64 Ivl=0ms
I:* If#= 7 Alt= 0 #EPs= 3 Cls=ff(vend.) Sub=fb Prot=ff Driver=qmi_wwan
